<p>Chief Minister of the Eastern Province, Sivanesathurai Chandrakanthan (alias Pillaiyan), all 
of whom are linked to numerous allegations of serious crimes during the armed conflict.25 
Both Karuna and Pillaiyan were former LTTE commanders who subsequently formed the 
