Amnesty International, Sri Lanka report, available from www.amnesty.org/en/region/sri-lanka/report-
</p><p>2010. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>26
  S/AC.51/2007/9. See also Human Rights Watch, &#8220;Sri Lanka: Karuna Group Abducts Children for 
</p>
<p>Combat&#8221;, 25 January 2007, available from www.hrw.org/news/2007/01/23/sri-lanka-karuna-group-
